== How to use pypi mirror? ==

* If using PIP, crate PIP config file: /root/.pip/pip.conf

    [global]
    index-url = http://192.168.99.10/pypi/

* If using easy_install, check mirror config in /root/.pydistutils.cfg

    [easy_install]
    index_url = http://192.168.99.10/pypi/

* If using easy_install, pass PYPI environ for Makefile

    $ sudo PYPI=http://192.168.99.10/pypi/ ALLOWHOSTS=192.168.99.10 make all

